responses: {"Q0":"Some of the melodies were quite lengthy, longer than I would give for dictations. My answers regarding number of times a melody was heard was influenced by this. How difficult second year students would find it were based more on the difficulty of the material. I wondered a bit about \"well formed.\" Many were well formed according to tonal music but quite boring. I didn't take the quality of the melody into account, simply the grammar and syntax."}
